COMM: With their ability to crunch through

00:00:23.039 --> 00:00:30.039
human bone in a single bite, getting up close
and personal with a 1,300lb grizzly bear is

00:00:30.039 --> 00:00:31.730
not for the faint hearted.

00:00:32.500 --> 00:00:35.660
But for 71-year-old Doug Seus, coming face-to-face

00:00:35.660 --> 00:00:39.500
with the fearsome predators is all in a days work.

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:42.500
